Jumping Challenge - Box Jump 1

Demonstrate a Box jump (vertical) onto a knee-height block/wall/obstacle with any number of steps into the movement.

You must takeoff two feet simultaneously and land on top of the obstacle with two feet at the same time.

Repeat three times.

-- Rules of Challenge --

Rule 1 description : The height of the wall must be knee-height or greater.
Rule 2 description : Three repetitions in total.
Rule 3 description : Must land both feet at the same time.
Rule 4 description : Must take off both feet at the same time.
Rule 5 description : Finish facing the same direction as your starting direction.
